<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_408_r1l9"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> . als eẅr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> dıe <expan>anlangu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> der ſteẅre dıe etlıchen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_408_r1l10"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> vnd der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>leẅt<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd <expan>gut<ex>en</ex></expan> / von <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>amptleẅt<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_408_r1l12">beſchehen 
<add><ab facs="#facs_408_r1l11">yecʒ aber </ab></add> / <expan>aufgeſlag<ex>en</ex></expan> hat / Hat vns <expan>Gunth<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Müncʒmeıſt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_408_r1l13">vnd Ratgeſell fürbracht / wıe Jm in dem aufſlag den eẅr gnade </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_408_r1l15"><expan>am<ex>m</ex></expan> erſten geben hett 
<add><ab facs="#facs_408_r1l14">von der gemeın des dorffs ʒum ʒıegelanger </ab></add> an <expan>etlıche<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ſeıne<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>güt<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vnd weıngerte ʒu ʒeıl </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_408_r1l16"><expan>beſweru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> vnd <expan>v<ex>er</ex>pott</expan> geſchehen ſeyn / <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> wır <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>hofm<ex>eiſter</ex>r</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_408_r1l17"><expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd gebetten haben / <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> ſeine <expan>güt<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_408_r1l18">ſein bey <expan>ſölıche<ex>n</ex></expan> aufſlag auch <expan>beleıbe<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd dıe verpott darauf </ab>
