<ab facs="#facs_408_r1l20"><expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> wır eẅr <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade mıt fleıſʒ . mıt <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>amptleẅt<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_408_r1l21">den <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> ʒu beſtellen / daʒ des <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan> vnd <expan>Ratgeſelle<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>güt<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
